@NODE arexx "IsdnMon.Guide: Arexx"}

Quit			-> Quits IsdnMon without any requester
@{U}                                                                         @{UU}

Disconnect [Unit]	-> Disconnects the given Unit. The Unit
			   MUST be the Number, not the Name.
@{U}                                                                         @{UU}

IsCarrier [Unit]	-> Returns 'CARRIER' if the specified
			   Unit is connected or 'NO CARRIER' if not.
@{U}                                                                         @{UU}

IsNumber [Unit]		-> Returns the Number the Unit is connected
			   with. If unknown, IsdnMon returns
			   'NUMBER UNKNOWN' or 'NO CONNECT' if not
			   connected.
@{U}                                                                         @{UU}

TXBytes [Unit		-> Returns the number of transmitted Bytes
@{U}                                                                         @{UU}

RXBytes [Unit]		-> Returns the number of received Bytes 
@{U}                                                                         @{UU}

GetOnlineTime [Unit]	-> Returns the Time, how long the
			   unit is already online (in seconds)
@{U}                                                                         @{UU}

GetCurrency [Unit]	-> Returns the currency for the connection as
			   string (e.g. $0.60)
@{U}                                                                         @{UU}

@ENDNODE



